 }
 
 /// Minimum meters the shipped policy must close toward the far chase ball for a release
-/// to publish (`rl-train eval --min-progress`). Calibrated 2026-07-06 on the 9 m default
-/// ball: the collapsed mlp512x3-s2 brain that reached the TV measures 0.12 m
-/// (deterministic across runs); live journey brains measure 3.5–8.9 m. 1.0 sits ≥8×
